> Two employees who publicly defended diversity initiatives have found themselves targeted by online mobs and out of a job soon after.

&nbsp;

> Riot hosted an informational event at a Seattle gaming conference exclusively for women and gender nonbinary people. Such networking sessions are a common tool for companies looking to diversify

&nbsp;

> &ldquo;I feel a lot of people are silently giving up,&rdquo; one current employee said. &ldquo;There&rsquo;s a lot of sadness and resignation to the fact that nothing permanent or meaningful is going to happen.&rdquo;

